<plot>KOM is a short movie that tells the story of an old woman living in close company with her memories of the past. Serious, philosophical and dramatic topics are joined with fresh and energetic images, music and sounds. KOM combines the painful and poetic sides of life in a mind-bending script.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?283405</url></doc>
